These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, trike, boat, van, airplane
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, pakistani, russian
5 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse, rabbit, snake
City: miami, colone, berlin, liverpool, paris
 1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is the person driving the airplane##1
 3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the pakistani##1
 6. the british is the person driving the trike##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the british is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the bus is on the right of the british##1
10. the person driving the van is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
11. the owner of the hamster is the person traveling to miami##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Transport         | trike  | bus    | van | boat    | airplane  |
| Nationality   | british  | brazilian | chinese | pakistani | russian  |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | rabbit  | hamster   | horse    |
| City         | berlin | liverpool    | colone | miami  | paris |

