.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cucumber, kiwi, lettuce, watermelon
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, green, blue, coral, orange
5 different games are played: monopoly, chess, canasta, scrabble, whist
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the person who likes coral is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the mexican is the person playing chess##1
 3. the indonesian is on the right of the russian##1
 4. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the russian is the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person eating cucumber is in the middle##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the mexican##1
12. the person eating kiwi is the person who likes green##1
13. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Food          | kiwi        | watermelon | cucumber     | lettuce      | artichoke  |
| Color           | green   | blue | orange    | coral | ebony |
| Game   | canasta | scrabble     | whist | monopoly    | chess  |
| Nationality   | russian     | indonesian | argentine    | spanish      | mexican    |

