.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite, tea, water
5 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, go, whist, snooker
There are 5 different favourite colors: emerald, orange, green, black, coral
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, scooter, snowmobile, train
 1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing go##1
 3. the person who likes emerald is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 5. the person who likes green is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 9. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
11. the person who likes green is the person playing canasta##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the person drinking tea is the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | tea          | sprite  | milk       | fanta     | water      |
| Game         | mah-jongg | snooker | whist  | go   | canasta    |
| Color   | orange        | coral | emerald | black    | green   |
| Transport     | helicopter   | scooter | train      | quad-bike | snowmobile |

