.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, fish, hamster, goat
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, horror, scientific, superhero, time-travel
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, gospel, indie, pop, techno
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, december, june, may, january
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the fan of country##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 3. the fan of gospel is the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the fan of country is the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the owner of the goat is the fan of indie##1
11. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Pet          | hamster        | goldfish       | fish | frog   | goat  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | scientific | horror | drama   | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | techno     | gospel | country | indie     |
| Birthday     | february        | december        | january    | may    | june      |

