 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the person who likes grey is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
10. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
