There are 5 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch, egyptian, french
5 different games are played: bridge, whist, backgammon, go, billiard
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person eating raspberry is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is the australian##1
 5. the french is on the far right##1
 6. the egyptian is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the dutch is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person playing whist is on the left of the person drinking water##1
10. the egyptian is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
11. the person drinking fanta is the person eating cherry##1
12. the person playing go is the british##1
13. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |     5     |
| Food          | cherry     | lettuce  | raspberry | banana     | artichoke |
| Beverage           | fanta   | water | sprite     | almond-milk | lemonade |
| Nationality   | australian | british  | dutch     | egyptian   | french    |
| Game     | whist       | go     | billiard     | backgammon      | bridge  |

