 3. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the person eating strawberry is the owner of the turtle##1
 7. the person drinking water is the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
10. the person eating nectarine is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the owner of the lizard##1
12. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
13. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
14. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
