 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the pakistani is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the dutch is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
12. the person watching romance movies is the person traveling to london##1
13. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola       | milk         | juice  | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | scientific | martial-arts | crime  | western  |
| City   | london    | berlin    | edinburgh        | boston | paris     |
| Nationality           | chinese | thai      | malaysian       | dutch   | pakistani   |

