.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda, sprite
5 different games are played: go, monopoly, domino, canasta, mah-jongg
There 5 different types of food: broccoli, zucchini, peas, cauliflower, lime
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, snowmobile, train, tram
 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing canasta is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 4. the person playing go is the person eating lime##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person playing domino is the person eating zucchini##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the person playing go is on the far right##1
12. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
13. the person eating broccoli is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | milk    | cola       | sprite |
| Game   | domino           | monopoly   | mah-jongg   | canasta       | go  |
| Food   | zucchini       | broccoli | peas | cauliflower     | lime   |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | scooter   | train   | helicopter | tram   |

 